urlText: Central station: Southern tunnel temporarily closed
content:
From Thursday 2 until Saturday 25 January, the Southern Tunnel at Central Station will be temporarily closed due to Sydney Metro works.

To access Platforms 4 - 23 please follow signs and use the Suburban Tunnel or the Northern Concourse.

For more information about Sydney Metro Works, visit sydneymetro.info
subtitle: Central station: Southern tunnel temporarily closed
